---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
    <div class="footer-container">
        <div class="philosophy">
            <div class="footer-group">
                <p class="en-f">We spend our lives searching for an order that carries warmth.</p>
                <p class="zh-f">我们终其一生，不过是在寻找一种有温度的秩序。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-group">
                <p class="en-f">To find softness within the sharp, and wholeness within the incomplete.</p>
                <p class="zh-f">在锐利中寻圆润，在缺失中见完整。</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="footer-divider" />

        <div class="contact-zone">
            <a href="mailto:i@kingsleyqi.com?subject=Hello%20Kingsley" class="mail-link">
                <span class="mail-label">Connect /</span> i@kingsleyqi.com
            </a>
            
            <p class="copyright">
                &copy; {today.getFullYear()} Kingsley Qi. 
                <span class="location">Santo Tomas, Batangas</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    footer {
        padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem 1.5rem;
        background: #ffffff; /* 放弃渐变，回归纯净的白 */
        border-top: 1px solid #f9f9f9;
    }

    .footer-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .philosophy {
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .footer-group {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* 英文：柔和的灰，衬线斜体 */
    .en-f {
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #aaa;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    /* 中文：深色，高间距，呼吸感 */
    .zh-f {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: #333;
        font-weight: 300;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .footer-divider {
        width: 30px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        border: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    /* 邮箱设计：去掉了刺眼的蓝色 */
    .mail-link {
        font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; /* 增加一点技术感 */
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #222;
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .mail-label {
        color: #bbb;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .mail-link:hover {
        opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .copyright {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: #ccc;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .location {
        margin-left: 1rem;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .zh-f { font-size: 0.95rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
        .en-f { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    }
</style>
